Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:29.73,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}想要守护你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:36.60,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}然后再次 去往没有悲伤的时间轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:42.91,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{be2\fad(100,100)}逐渐吞噬消失 孤独的观测者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从2036年回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是时间旅行者
